---
title: Lamb & Mushroom Bacon Pie with Filo Pastry & Red Wine Jus
description: There is no more comforting meal than a warm, hearty pie, fresh from the oven! Tonight’s feast wraps tender lamb, savoury
mushrooms, and rich jus in layers of golden, flaky filo pastry. It’s perfect for those nights when you need a warm hug on a plate!
This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.
